@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_jtzqve(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (v0 / wp.sin(tmp))
    v1 = (v2 + (wp.exp(v1 + 0.83) + (tmp + 0.27 + tmp + 0.91)))
    v0 = wp.exp(0.13)
    tmp = (0.27 + v0)
    v1 = (wp.abs(v0) - ((v2 + 0.07 - v0 + 0.96) + 0.50))
    v1 = (v0 / (wp.abs(v0 + 0.32) + v2))
    v2 = v1
    v0 = v2
    data[tid] = v0
